# PR Workflow Rules

Complements the PR workflow defined in AGENTS.md. These rules add the AskQuestion continuation pattern to PR operations.

## PR Review Flow

When given a PR link to review:

1. Run `gh pr view` and `gh pr diff` (do NOT switch branches)
2. Analyze the changes thoroughly
3. Present findings
4. End with AskQuestion:

```
AskQuestion({
  title: "PR Review Complete",
  questions: [
    {
      id: "action",
      prompt: "Review complete. What should we do with this PR?",
      options: [
        { id: "land", label: "Land it - create integration branch and merge" },
        { id: "request-changes", label: "Request changes - leave review comments" },
        { id: "approve", label: "Approve as-is" },
        { id: "discuss", label: "Discuss specific concerns before deciding" },
        { id: "custom", label: "Other action" }
      ]
    }
  ]
})
```

## PR Landing Flow

When landing a PR (per AGENTS.md):

1. Create temp branch from main
2. Merge PR branch (prefer squash for messy history, rebase for clean)
3. Add changelog entry with PR # and contributor thanks
4. Run full gate: `pnpm build && pnpm check && pnpm test`
5. Commit, merge back to main, delete temp branch
6. Check if contributor needs adding to clawtributors
7. End with AskQuestion:

```
AskQuestion({
  title: "PR Landed",
  questions: [
    {
      id: "post-merge",
      prompt: "PR merged successfully. What's next?",
      options: [
        { id: "comment", label: "Leave merge comment on the PR with SHA details" },
        { id: "clawtributors", label: "Update clawtributors (new contributor)" },
        { id: "next-pr", label: "Review another PR" },
        { id: "release", label: "Start release process" },
        { id: "custom", label: "Other" }
      ]
    }
  ]
})
```

## PR Creation Flow

When creating a PR:

1. Check git status, diff, and log
2. Draft PR summary
3. Before creating, AskQuestion to confirm:

```
AskQuestion({
  title: "PR Ready to Create",
  questions: [
    {
      id: "confirm",
      prompt: "PR draft ready. Confirm or adjust?",
      options: [
        { id: "create", label: "Create it as-is" },
        { id: "edit-title", label: "Edit the title" },
        { id: "edit-body", label: "Edit the description" },
        { id: "add-labels", label: "Add labels before creating" },
        { id: "draft", label: "Create as draft PR" },
        { id: "custom", label: "Other" }
      ]
    }
  ]
})
```
